title: Motrhigh 80s pop ballad mix
info:
Until now, I was lonely.
My world was empty; I was nobody.
Now you have entered, my life has changed:
I don't feel bitter, I don't feel rage.
But now I've got to leave.
I'm not guilty. I don't need a reprieve.
I see your face; the tears flow.
I'm innocent. I have to go.
Babe, I love you (I love you)
I need you, I adore you (Adore you)
I need you, I adore you (Adore you)
But I just can't stay.

Babe, I love you (I love you)
I need you, I adore you (Adore you)

But I just can't stay.
